{"tid":1168904,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"隨母象開工被遊客騎 小象不支倒地仍要行","createTime":"2019-05-24T04:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T12:44:07.000Z","uid":3090,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f4535044b0cd8c66daa4dbed217ad3415cb4ea2d","tid":1168904,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3WsvWAL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3WsvWAL.png&h=223d7ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n一名遊客上周在泰國芭堤雅旅遊時，目擊一隻跟隨母象讓遊客騎乘的小象，疑似受到虐待。<br />\n<br />\n那位在緬甸當教師的菲律賓人，到東芭樂園旅遊時，拍到一隻供遊客騎的大象，以繩頸連頸繫着約１歲的小象一起行，其間小象倒地，有途人說：「噢，不。牠很累。」母象哄小象站起來，牠聽母象話，勉為其難站起繼續「開工」。<br />\n<br />\n那位遊客說，園內很多母象繫着幼象，載遊客四處行。當天氣溫40℃，在烈日下，遊客坐得舒服，象卻就行辛苦。她表示關注象的福祉是否得到照顧。<br />\n<br />\n園方否認幼象體力不支或受到虐待，稱所有象都健康且受善待，象的身體但凡出毛病，都有獸醫照顧。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"968c2c8993099cbadcbe33fc21b6260ade486f15","tid":1168904,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"啲00後唔捱得"},{"pid":"a175608d62d7cbb0f78e5cdaefbf4af2c0706499","tid":1168904,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"968c2c8993099cbadcbe33fc21b6260ade486f15","tid":1168904,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"啲00後唔捱得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:25:17.000Z","msg":"10 後喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8edb58bdb36d832f82f784e2fdf10f91936575","tid":1168904,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T04:27:13.000Z","msg":"象仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a89060c563b4ffc60f223e36a00064fc9e379a9e","tid":1168904,"u